---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const formAction = "https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id";
---

<BaseLayout title="Share Your Story | Dare to Break Free">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Share Your Story</p>
    <h1>Your story deserves care, shape and a listening ear.</h1>
    <p class="lede">A gentle invitation for people who are ready to explore the story they have lived and the meaning they want to make from it.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section two-column">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">The invitation</p>
      <h2>Start with the truth. Then find the thread.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="stack">
      <p>Share Your Story is for people carrying a lived experience they want to understand, preserve, or pass on. It may become a written piece, a keepsake, a talk, a letter, or simply a clearer version of the truth.</p>
      <p>Bring the raw material. The work is to listen closely, honour what matters, and shape it without sanding away the life in it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="form-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Enquire</p>
      <h2>Tell me where you are starting from</h2>
      <p>Use the form below to send a first note. The Formspree endpoint can be swapped in as soon as it is ready.</p>
    </div>
    <form class="contact-form" action={formAction} method="POST">
      <label>
        Name
        <input name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
      </label>
      <label>
        Email
        <input name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required />
      </label>
      <label>
        What would you like help with?
        <textarea name="message" rows="7" required></textarea>
      </label>
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="share-your-story" />
      <button class="button" type="submit">Send enquiry</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
